Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:47.76,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,遠ざかる 星の 彼方を さすらう魂よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:49.67,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,聞えるか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:23:02.02,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠に 続く この銀河で 安らかに眠れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:06.13,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,別離のレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:11.87,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君へのレクイエム Sing along
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:20.50,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,讃える歌声 忘れ得ぬメモリー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:25.35,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,And we’ll never forget your name
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:28.02,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:34.90,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,さらば友よ 今は悲しみ 尽きないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:42.46,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,またいつか この星の海で きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:46.04,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,Pray for the earth　その誓いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:49.65,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,Pray for the dream　その理想を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:58.67,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh Oh Oh Oh yeah last forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:47.76,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流于遥远的星球彼岸的灵魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:49.67,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:23:02.02,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,请在这无垠的银河中 安息长眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:06.13,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,分别的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:11.87,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,送给你的安魂曲 Sing along
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:20.50,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,用赞美的旋律 歌颂难忘的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:25.35,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,And we’ll never forget your name
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:28.02,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:34.90,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,别了挚友 虽然我现在悲痛万分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:42.46,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 定会在这片星海中重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,
